Package com.iplanet.services.comm.client

Interface NotificationHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PolicyNotificationHandler, SessionNotificationHandler
    public interface NotificationHandler
    The NotificationHandler interface needs to be implemented by high level services and applications in order to be able to receive notifications from the Platform Low Level API. The handler registration is done through the PLLClient class.
    See Also:
    Notification, PLLClient
